cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use NLPstudio in academic work, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "NLPstudio: Tools for Social Science Text Analysis, Corpus Management, and Topic Modeling"
abstract: >-
  NLPstudio provides a streamlined and high-performance workflow for social
  science text analysis with structured and unstructured corpora, including
  corpus creation from JSON, tokenization, parsing, readability and similarity
  measures, and a unified topic-modeling API across text2vec, topicmodels,
  seededlda, stm, and topicmodels.etm.
authors:
